<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">
  It's been a while since you've visited ReZum. Your resume toolkit is ready and waiting to help you land your next role.
</p>

<% if @user.credits_remaining > 0 %>
  <div style="background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1e40af;">
      You still have <strong><%= @user.credits_remaining %> credit<%= 's' if @user.credits_remaining != 1 %></strong> available!
    </p>
  </div>
<% end %>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">Here's what you can do:</p>
<ul style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px;">
  <li>Upload and optimize a resume for a new role</li>
  <li>Generate a tailored cover letter</li>
  <li>Check your ATS compatibility score</li>
</ul>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 16px;">
  <a href="<%= dashboard_url %>" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed); color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;">
    Come Back to ReZum
  </a>
</div>
